reviewText: Legacy journey is a great follow up to FPU.  If you are in (or close to) step 5,6 and 7, this is for you.
Cash grab. Does not offer any new information not already covered in FPU. If you've already taken FPU, then just review that and save your money
i am in week one of seven. Dave is engaging and winsome unlike the personality we are exposed to on the radio. My wife are doing the homework and looking forward to the next class.
